Changelog for SHE_GST Galaxy Simulations toolkit

Changes from v1.6 to v1.8
=========================

API Changes
-----------

- Added support for wcs_theta, wcs_g1, and wcs_g2 options to config files

Dependency Changes
------------------

- Now depends on SHE_PPT 1.0

Deprecated Features
-------------------

Bug Fixes
---------

- Fixed units bug preventing background galaxies from being rendered

New Features
------------

- Added support for WCS rotation and shear

New config features
-------------------

Miscellaneous
-------------

- Fixed default sky background level to be more realistic

Changes from v1.4 to v1.6
=========================

API Changes
-----------

- Output data now matches how we expect to get data from SC4

Dependency Changes
------------------

- Now depends on SHE_PPT 0.8

Deprecated Features
-------------------

Bug Fixes
---------

New Features
------------

New config features
-------------------

Miscellaneous
-------------


Changes from v1.2 to v1.4
=========================

API Changes
-----------

Dependency Changes
------------------

- Now depends on Elements 5.2.2
- Now depends on SHE_PPT 0.6

Deprecated Features
-------------------

Bug Fixes
---------

New Features
------------

New config features
-------------------

Miscellaneous
-------------

- Upgraded to use python 3


Changes from v1.1 to v1.2
=========================

API Changes
-----------


Dependency Changes
------------------

- Galsim with the InclinedSersic profile is now required (v1.5 or master)


Deprecated Features
-------------------

- Removed deprecated checks for InclinedSersic profile in Galsim; it's not required

Bug Fixes
---------

New Features
------------

- Now generates full set of mock data (image, PSF image, detections table, PSF table,
  segmentation map, noisemap, mask, AOCS time series, astrometry, mission time) in
  expected formats

New config features
-------------------

- Allows specification of workdir and logdir, as expected by the pipeline runner. The
  workdir will also be passed to the C++ code and used as the location of cache files

Miscellaneous
-------------

- Re-licensed code to Euclid SGS under LGPL
- Added README

--Versions prior to 1.1 not tracked in changelog--